Titolo: BlazBlue: Clone Phantasma

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: BlazBlue: Clone Phantasma, released in Japan as BlazBlue: Clonephantasma (ぶれいぶるー くろーんふぁんたずま, BureiBurū: Kurōnfantazuma), is a 2012 3D arena fighting video game developed by Arc System Works, released as an eShop application for the Nintendo 3DS. It is the sequel to BlayzBloo: Super Melee Brawlers Battle Royale. The game was released in Japan on December 26, 2012 and North America on August 21, 2014.